    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting when you choose this tradition at 3rd level, you can use your ki to duplicate the effects of certain spells. As an action, you can spend 2 ki points to cast @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.95HlMKeNkm1x8LIQ]{Darkness}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.EcbviTRdyVBHX78g]{Darkvision}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.67lR5mwQRa9HKAGa]{Pass without Trace}, or @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.IWxKwBugJfls3V7S]{Silence}, without providing material components. Additionally, you gain the @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.vsLp2emCFTGf811b]{Minor Illusion} cantrip if you don't already know it.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: Add the above spells to your character and make the following changes:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Set Spell Preparation Mode to Innate Spellcasting</em></li>\n<li><em>Set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Ki: 2</em></li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
